00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:01,120
deal with me first.

563
00:35:01,680 --> 00:35:03,480
Just you and me, alright?

564
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,640
Oh, hey...

565
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:24,000
So, babe, did you find Qin?

566
00:35:24,040 --> 00:35:26,160
Yeah, but I lost him.

567
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:27,720
Ran into that guy instead.

568
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:28,600
His name is Duang.

569
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:31,960
And how was he?

570
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:33,000
Good-looking?

571
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:35,720
Yeah, and he's kinda funny.

572
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:39,600
That's great. Take him as well.

573
00:35:39,640 --> 00:35:40,800
That way, we've got a full pair.

574
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,400
The senior came looking for me again.

575
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:46,480
I don't wanna perform anymore.

576
00:35:47,680 --> 00:35:50,600
So...where did that senior go?

577
00:35:51,040 --> 00:35:52,040
Lost you already?

578
00:35:52,600 --> 00:35:54,320
I had that guy
who keeps following me block him.

579
00:35:55,560 --> 00:35:57,800
That fan is still following you around?

580
00:35:58,640 --> 00:36:01,480
I said to him,
"Why are you following Qin?"

581
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:03,120
You know, isn't that cool?

582
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:05,920
So cool.

583
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:08,440
"You too can become a hero."

584
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:12,040
And then?

585
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,320
Nothing happened.

586
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,840
He suddenly asked for my name.

587
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:16,920
It felt sketchy,
like he was trying to sell me something.

588
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,320
So I told him my name
and rushed over to you guys.

589
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:21,920
Wait, so you
only talked to Qin that much?

590
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,160
That was four whole sentences.

591
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,880
Four sentences, dude.

592
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,560
That's longer than a chant.

593
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,320
Don't disrespect me like that.

594
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,680
It reminded me of that fortune teller.

595
00:36:33,720 --> 00:36:35,120
Remember what I told you?

596
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,480
She was right.

597
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,240
She said Qin would ask me for help,

598
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,840
and then he actually did.

599
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:43,480
And I was so close to him, like...

600
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:45,960
face-to-face close.

601
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,760
Close enough to make a finger heart.

602
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:48,720
Cut it out.

603
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,040
You're exaggerating.

604
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:51,200
I'm not.

605
00:36:51,240 --> 00:36:53,080
I'm sure
the rest of the results are right, too.

606
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:56,000
How am I supposed
to confess to Qin now?

607
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:58,440
My heart's already all his.

608
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,640
Just confess already.

609
00:37:00,680 --> 00:37:03,440
If you like him so much,
then just tell him.

610
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:04,800
I can't do that.

611
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:05,680
I'm serious about this.

612
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:07,960
Come on, just say it.

613
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:10,240
You're a born lover.

614
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:11,480
You totally got this.

615
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:13,720
Even though
the assignment's due today,

616
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:16,000
you're here thinking about him
instead of submitting anything.

617
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:18,000
That's harsh.

618
00:37:18,040 --> 00:37:19,520
I'm being real, though.

619
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,640
So go on, just confess.

620
00:37:21,180 --> 00:37:22,560
You don't understand.

621
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:24,480
Qin's super popular, you know.

622
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:26,200
People always come on to him.

623
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,680
"You don't understand.

624
00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:30,480
Qin's super popular, you know.

625
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:34,360
I bet people always come on to him."

626
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,680
You think only you know that?

627
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:37,320
If you wanna confess,
just do it already.

628
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,440
Don't play games.

629
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:43,720
What?

630
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:47,280
Here's what you do.

631
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:50,880
Just tell him straight up
that you don't want to perform anymore.

632
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,640
Then he'll stop bugging you like this.

633
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:56,600
Yeah, I'll tell him.

634
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,480
Hey, guys.

635
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,160
Wanna go to the Loy Krathong Festival?

636
00:38:09,080 --> 00:38:10,440
Yeah, I can go.

637
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,160
Qin, what about you?

638
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,360
I don't want to. It's hot.

639
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:20,160
You don't need to stay too long.

640
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:21,400
No, I don't wanna go.

641
00:38:22,040 --> 00:38:24,120
But there's a lot of stuff there.

642
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,680
Desserts and all that.

643
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:27,440
You can just go with me.

644
00:38:29,520 --> 00:38:30,520
No, but...

645
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,680
Didn't you say
you were craving desserts?

646
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,480
Bua loy, foi thong,

647
00:38:35,520 --> 00:38:37,920
custard bread, and things like that.

648
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,840
Doesn't that sound tempting?

649
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:50,920
Hey,

650
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:54,120
- What?
- you asked me how to confess, right?

651
00:38:54,160 --> 00:38:55,680
Yeah, what should I do?

652
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:57,360
Friends gotta have each other's backs.

653
00:38:57,960 --> 00:39:01,080
I've got a plan
for your confession, buddy.

654
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:04,960
Buddy...

655
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:08,320
- Buddy...
- That's what friends are for.

656
00:39:30,600 --> 00:39:31,920
- There he is.
- Where?

657
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:33,400
- Where is he?
- Let's go.

658
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:42,080
Who are you looking for?

659
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,840
The one I'm meeting.
Her name's Cherry.

660
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:46,400
Oh...

661
00:39:46,600 --> 00:39:49,240
So that's why
you wanted to come to this festival?

662
00:39:50,720 --> 00:39:52,400
No wonder you were so eager to come.

663
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:53,880
So, have you seen her?

664
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:56,960
I'll try texting her
to ask where she is.

665
00:39:58,400 --> 00:40:00,960
[Where are you?]

666
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:07,360
[I can see you now]

667
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:11,520
[You can only bring one friend]

668
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:14,800
[I want that one next to you]

669
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,440
We'll be right back.

670
00:40:17,680 --> 00:40:18,680
- Let's go, Qin.
- Oh...

671
00:40:20,520 --> 00:40:22,360
No, not that one.

672
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:23,960
[No, not that one]

673
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:25,160
Where are you going?

674
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:28,320
[No, not that one]

675
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:38,640
Who is he calling?

676
00:40:42,080 --> 00:40:43,880
You talk to him.

677
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:51,080
Hi, Cherry.

678
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:53,120
Where are you now?

679
00:40:55,160 --> 00:40:56,520
I can see you from here.

680
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:59,400
But don't bring that friend with you.

681
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:03,840
Yes.

682
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:05,920
My friend likes that friend of yours.

683
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:09,000
Okay, I'll see you.

684
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:10,880
Okay.

685
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,320
Alright.

686
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,240
What now?

687
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,400
We'll be right back, Qin.

688
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:17,880
- Just stroll around for now.
- What?

689
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:18,920
Come on, Kim.

690
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,600
Where are we going? What about Qin?

691
00:41:20,640 --> 00:41:21,600
What?

692
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:36,240
Go now. Win Qin's heart.

693
00:41:37,040 --> 00:41:37,960
- Come on.
- What?

694
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:39,400
You're sending me alone?

695
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:42,160
Dude, nobody confesses as a group.

696
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,200
Are you nuts?

697
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,000
Exactly.

698
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:46,080
Just stay here
until you're ready, then.

699
00:41:46,120 --> 00:41:47,800
Jamie and I
will buy you some time. Bye.

700
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,200
Come on, Jamie.

701
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:57,960
Qin...

702
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:17,480
[Where are you?]

703
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:24,040
Let's go back to Qin.

704
00:42:24,080 --> 00:42:25,200
Give me a moment.

705
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:27,200
No, I'm done.

706
00:42:27,240 --> 00:42:28,440
She's ditching you for sure.

707
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:29,200
Let's go.

708
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:31,560
Keep them busy. I'll let Duang know.

709
00:42:31,600 --> 00:42:32,680
Alright. Got it.

710
00:42:34,200 --> 00:42:36,000
[Where are you?
I can't find you]

711
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,800
Kim,

712
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,200
I think she's coming.

713
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,800
- Check this out.
- What?

714
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:46,080
Qin, can I take a picture with you?

715
00:42:47,120 --> 00:42:48,200
Can I get a picture?

716
00:42:48,640 --> 00:42:49,880
Please excuse me.

717
00:42:50,040 --> 00:42:51,040
Sorry. I'm in a hurry.

718
00:42:52,640 --> 00:42:53,640
Hey!

719
00:43:05,560 --> 00:43:06,560
Uh...

720
00:43:07,140 --> 00:43:08,680
I was calling him.

721
00:43:08,880 --> 00:43:11,430
- Oh...
- Oh...

722
00:43:11,470 --> 00:43:12,150
Not us.

723
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:13,800
Not me.

724
00:43:15,400 --> 00:43:17,120
Well...

725
00:43:17,560 --> 00:43:18,560
I...

726
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:22,360
My buddy likes you.

727
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:23,920
Your buddy?

728
00:43:32,720 --> 00:43:33,720
My name is 'Buddy.'

729
00:43:39,240 --> 00:43:40,400
I'm sick of it.

730
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,680
Another one like this.

731
00:43:42,080 --> 00:43:43,760
Hey, hold on. Calm down.

732
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:45,760
I'm Duang. Give me a chance.

733
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:48,160
So is your name 'Buddy' or 'Duang'?

734
00:43:49,040 --> 00:43:50,040
It's Duang.

735
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:54,520
Would you mind

736
00:43:55,800 --> 00:43:57,320
if I floated my krathong with you?

737
00:44:01,800 --> 00:44:03,160
Just say what you want.

738
00:44:04,600 --> 00:44:06,000
Can I try to win your heart?

739
00:44:07,670 --> 00:44:10,040
No, I'm going to win your heart.

740
00:44:10,160 --> 00:44:11,280
I'm not asking for your permission.

741
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,640
I just want to let you know.

742
00:44:17,440 --> 00:44:19,520
Then tell me,
why do you want to win my heart?

743
00:44:19,560 --> 00:44:20,280
You've got fair skin!

744
00:44:20,320 --> 00:44:20,880
What?

745
00:44:20,920 --> 00:44:22,520
Stop it, or you'll ruin his chance.

746
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:25,240
Amazing.

747
00:44:28,240 --> 00:44:30,200
I was trying to say
you have perfect skin.

748
00:44:31,240 --> 00:44:33,360
You've got beautiful eyes,

749
00:44:33,680 --> 00:44:34,930
a stunning nose,

750
00:44:35,840 --> 00:44:37,280
pretty lips,

751
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:39,000
and even...

752
00:44:40,080 --> 00:44:41,680
perfect legs.

753
00:44:55,680 --> 00:44:57,880
I'm sorry. I didn't mean to say that.
The truth is I like you...

754
00:45:03,060 --> 00:45:04,320
because you sing so beautifully.

755
00:45:12,560 --> 00:45:14,120
You're incredibly charming,
you know that?

756
00:45:16,720 --> 00:45:18,440
I feel like I've been enchanted

757
00:45:18,480 --> 00:45:19,800
all because of your voice.

758
00:46:03,040 --> 00:46:04,360
Good luck with that, then.

759
00:46:28,440 --> 00:46:30,440
- Don't die just yet.
- It's just the beginning.

760
00:46:31,480 --> 00:46:33,480
Yay!

761
00:46:33,680 --> 00:46:35,080
This is so embarrassing.

762
00:46:35,360 --> 00:46:36,160
- Hey!
- Hey!

763
00:47:04,840 --> 00:47:05,600
I've got it!

764
00:47:05,640 --> 00:47:07,040
My plans to make Qin mine.

765
00:47:07,080 --> 00:47:09,440
But there's only a thin line
between pursuing and stalking.

766
00:47:09,480 --> 00:47:11,320
Why are you
so madly in love with him?

767
00:47:11,360 --> 00:47:13,400
Typically, a dog barks
at a plane, right?

768
00:47:13,440 --> 00:47:14,320
But suddenly,

769
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:15,880
the plane opens the door
and lets the dog in.

770
00:47:15,920 --> 00:47:17,040
He gave me the chance himself.

771
00:47:17,080 --> 00:47:18,160
I've gotta do my best.

772
00:47:18,200 --> 00:47:20,120
If he gets uncomfortable,
then you're a stalker.

773
00:47:20,160 --> 00:47:21,180
With how he's pursuing you,

774
00:47:21,220 --> 00:47:22,080
are you uncomfortable?

775
00:47:22,280 --> 00:47:24,280
Do you know that
you're causing people trouble?

776
00:47:24,320 --> 00:47:25,680
But I want to help.

777
00:47:25,720 --> 00:47:26,760
You can, by leaving it to me.

778
00:47:27,760 --> 00:47:29,720
It's too early for me to give up.

779
00:47:29,840 --> 00:47:31,360
Prepare to be mine!

780
